last_episode_to_air.name: Ultima Lucha Cuatro Pt. 2
last_episode_to_air.overview: El Dragon Azteca Jr. vs. Fenix; The Mack vs. Mil Muertes in a Death Match; Johnny Mundo vs. Matanza; Pentagón Dark vs. Marty "The Moth" in a Cero Miedo Match; The Order sets their plan in motion to destroy the Seven Aztec Tribes.

name: Lucha Underground
overview: Lucha Underground introduces U.S. audiences to the high-flying, explosive moves of lucha libre. An ancient combat tradition, watch as good and evil wage war in a gritty battleground called “The Temple.”

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Darkness has taken over the temple. With the stakes higher than ever, the luchadores return to square off in combat. As a bevy of new competitors arrive, it will take more than honor and strength to remain on top at Lucha Underground.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: Now that Dario Cueto has been released from prison after being arrested for the murder of Mr. Cisco, the mysterious Lucha Underground Temple is back in business. Dario is more confident than ever in his brother, the undefeated Lucha Underground Champion, the Monster Matanza Cueto and his quest for violent domination and the destruction of the seven ancient Aztec tribes. Now while one hero must take a dark path, others will have to make even greater sacrifices if they hope to save themselves and the world.

episodes.name: Welcome to the Temple
episodes.overview: In the series premiere of Lucha Underground, owner and promoter Dario Cueto opens his “Temple” to the best fighters from around the world, to compete for a 100k bonus. Watch as the masked heroes and villains battle it out in the Temple.

episodes.name: Los Demonios
episodes.overview: Johnny Mundo and Prince Puma are out for revenge on Big Ryck and his crew. Chavo teams with Sexy Star and takes on Son of Havoc & Ivelisse. Blue Demon Jr. is confronted by Catrina who warns him of 1000 Deaths… Mil Muertes. Chavo Guerro seeks revenge.

episodes.name: Crossing the Border
episodes.overview: Konnan brings Cueto the best talent from Mexico, sets main event Fenix vs Drago vs Pentagon Jr. El Mariachi Loco takes on Mascarita Segrada. Chavo explains his actions. Konnan warns Chavo that Mexico is coming for him. Ricky Mandell vs Mil Muertes.

episodes.name: Thrill of the Hunt
episodes.overview: Sexy Star returns to take on Ivelisse. Cueto confronts Drago, sets match against King Cuerno. Konnan warns Puma to not get involved in main event Mundo vs Big Ryck. Sexy Star vows revenge on Chavo.

episodes.name: Boyle Heights Street Fight
episodes.overview: Has Konnan made a mistake putting his young protégé Prince Puma in the ring with an experienced veteran and street fighter Big Ryck? Huge throw down in the temple tonight…Prince Puma vs Big Ryck Boyle Heights Street Fight…Everything is Legal…

episodes.name: The Key
episodes.overview: Big Ryck signs a contract with Dario Cueto. Pimpinela Escarlata answers Son of Havoc’s calling. Johnny Mundo wants his 100k back, steals Cueto’s key as an insurance policy. Sexy Star is back with Fenix to take on Chavo Guerrero and Pentagon Jr.

episodes.name: The Top of the Ladder
episodes.overview: Main Event: Three Way Ladder Match Prince Puma vs Johnny Mundo vs Big Ryck. Who will be the first Luchador to climb the ladder and retrieve the briefcase and walk out tonight with $100,000 dollars in cash courtesy of owner and promoter, Dario Cueto?

episodes.name: A Unique Opportunity
episodes.overview: Dario Cueto sets 10-Way match and Boyle Heights Battle Royal. Tonight, two luchadores will receive a unique opportunity that Cueto promises is even more valuable than the $100,000k he offered when he first opened his “Temple”.

episodes.name: Aztec Warfare
episodes.overview: Dario Cueto holds first ever Lucha Underground AZTEC WARFARE! Much like the ancient Aztecs had to fight for their survival… the champion will have to survive 19 other Luchadores. Who will earn the title of the first ever Lucha Underground Champion?

episodes.name: Law of the Jungle
episodes.overview: Our First Ever Lucha Underground Champion Prince Puma, will put his title on the line in a match against Fenix. Newcomers 4-Way Elimination Match Aerostar vs Argenis vs Angelico vs Cage. Chavo confronts Blue Demon Jr. Drago takes on King Cuerno.

episodes.name: Last Luchador Standing
episodes.overview: Last Luchador Standing Match, Drago vs King Cuerno. Their hunt for each other will finally come to an end tonight! No pinfalls, disqualifications, submissions or count-outs. Winner must incapacitate opponent until he can no longer answer 10 count.

episodes.name: They Call Him Cage
episodes.overview: Tonight Prince Puma puts his title on the line for the second time in just 3 weeks. Will Puma walk out of his hometown with the title again or will he be crushed by the man they call Cage? Main Event…Lucha Underground Championship Match…Puma vs Cage.

episodes.name: Johnny Mundo vs The Machine
episodes.overview: Cage looks to be the number one contender, but one of Lucha Undergrounds best fighters stands in his way. Surprise guest shows up to Dario Cueto’s temple.

episodes.name: A Shot of El Patron
episodes.overview: A new luchador arrives at the temple. Dario Cueto gives him a mic to address his fans and pledges to be the best Luchador in the World!

episodes.name: Eye for an Eye!
episodes.overview: Dario Cueto rewards the Crew with a No Disqualification Trios Match. Chavo finally faces Mil Muertes. Ivelisse takes matters into her own hands.

episodes.name: Caged Animals
episodes.overview: Cage looks to earn a Championship Match. Cueto offers another unique opportunity. Johnny Mundo seeks revenge.

episodes.name: A War Started in Mexico...
episodes.overview: A rivalry is renewed from Mexico, Dario Cueto pairs two luchadores with a history of bad blood. Huge Main Event.

episodes.name: No Escape
episodes.overview: Our Main Event gets even bigger. For the first time ever in Lucha Underground…A Steel Cage Match.

episodes.name: Grave Consequences
episodes.overview: MASSIVE main event to come, Grave Consequences is tonight, and the only way to win, put your opponent in a coffin!

episodes.name: The Art of War
episodes.overview: Two World Titles on the line… The Lucha Underground Championship is on the line and the stakes have never been higher… Boyle Heights Street Fight Main Event Championship Title Match.

episodes.name: Uno! Dos! Tres!
episodes.overview: New gold is up for grabs in the Temple. Dario Cueto sets up the Trios Titles Tournament to crown the first ever Lucha Underground Trios Tag Team Champions. The first match of Trios Tag Team Championship Tournament is TONIGHT!

episodes.name: Mask versus Mask
episodes.overview: Tonight, partners Sexy Star and Super Fly will compete against each other. Sacred masks on the line in our first ever Mask vs Mask Match. Champion Prince Puma takes on King Cuerno and Cueto’s Trios Tournament Continues.

episodes.name: Fire in the Cosmos
episodes.overview: Best of 5 Series Drago vs Aerostar will come to and end tonight. There’s one more spot left in next weeks Trios Title Match. With six of the best luchadores in the Temple, who will earn the last spot?

episodes.name: Trios Champions
episodes.overview: Tonight the first ever Lucha Underground Trios Champions will be crowned in a Three Way Trios Tag Team Elimination Match! Three teams have advanced but only one can walk away with the belts…The last surviving team wins the titles.

episodes.name: The Way of the Drago
episodes.overview: High stakes main event. Prince Puma faces Drago in a Champion vs Career match. Cueto vows to banish Drago from his Temple forever if he fails to beat defending champion Puma. 3 luchadores compete to be the new #1 Contender.

episodes.name: The Best in the Business
episodes.overview: The Crew is looking for revenge against the underdogs who beat them to become Trios Champions. Puma & Hernandez vs Cage & King Cuerno.   Alberto vs. Johnny Mundo, winner advances to a #1 Contender’s Match with Hernandez!

episodes.name: Ancient Medallions
episodes.overview: Seven top competitors go to battle over a mysterious medallion in a 7-way match.  Huge Main Event: Alberto El Patron vs Hernandez for the #1 Contender Title. The only way to win will be by pinfall or submission!

episodes.name: Shoots and Ladders
episodes.overview: The Trios Titles will be defended in a Ladder Match. The first person to climb the ladder and retrieve the championships will win the titles for their team. Meanwhile, Vampiro asks Johnny Mundo to explain his actions.

episodes.name: Fight to the Death
episodes.overview: Huge double Main Event. Fenix vs Mil Muertes Death Match. Prince Puma defends his Lucha Underground Championship Title against the #1 Contender, Hernandez. Vampiro sits down with Sexy Star.

episodes.name: Submit to the Master
episodes.overview: Argenis and Jack Evans fight in the Aztec Medallion Match; Sexy Star faces off against Pentagon Jr.

episodes.name: The Desolation of Drago
episodes.overview: Cueto sets a four-way match; Chavo Guerrero and Blue Demon Jr return to the temple.

episodes.name: All Night Long
episodes.overview: Prince Puma defends his title against Johnny Mundo; Cueto determines the victor.

episodes.name: Death vs. the Dragon
episodes.overview: Dario Cueto sets a rematch; Sexy Star vs Superfly; a 5-Way Aztec Medallion match with the winner earning a spot in UltimaLucha.

episodes.name: Gold and Guerreros
episodes.overview: Drago and Hernandez meet for the first time one on one. Texano has a score to settle. The Lucha Underground Championship is on the line…Prince Puma faces Chavo and his crew for the first time ever!

episodes.name: Fuel to the Fire
episodes.overview: Alberto El Patron and Mundo face each other; the two will team up with three others in a Atomicos Tag Team Match.

episodes.name: The Beginning of the End
episodes.overview: Pentagon Jr. is confronted by Vampiro; King Cuerno fights Killshot; Sexy Star meets Super Fly; Prince Puma prepares to face his Ultimalucha challenger, Mil Muertes.

episodes.name: PenUltimaLucha
episodes.overview: Cuerto reveals the meaning of the medallions; Texano vs. Mundo; Cage vs. Mack; the Battle Royal for the final medallion.

episodes.name: UltimaLucha: Part I
episodes.overview: The Machine Cage fights The Mack; Team Havoc faces the DOD; Drago fights Hernandez in Believers Backlash.

episodes.name: UltimaLucha: Part II
episodes.overview: Johnny Mundo fights Alberto El Patron; Vampiro fights Pentagon Jr.; the 7-Way Gift of the Gods Match; Prince Puma faces Mil Muertos.

episodes.name: A Much Darker Place
episodes.overview: The Luchadors return to compete, but with Dario Cueto on the run, darkness has taken over the temple.

episodes.name: The Dark & The Mysterious
episodes.overview: Prince Puma teams with an unlikely partner; Johnny Mundo returns to the temple with his sights set on the championship.

episodes.name: The Hunt is on...
episodes.overview: Catrina enlists King Cuerno to help her destroy Fenix; a new Luchadora debuts.

episodes.name: Cero Miedo
episodes.overview: Prince Puma takes on Pentagón Jr. for the first time; Rey Mysterio Jr. reveals the Cueto family history.

episodes.name: The Machine
episodes.overview: Johnny Mundo battles the Machine Cage; Texano returns for revenge against Chavo Guerrero and the crew.

episodes.name: Gift of the Gods Ladder Match
episodes.overview: King Cuerno defends his Gift of the Gods Championship against Fenix in a ladder match.

episodes.name: Death Comes in Threes
episodes.overview: Mil Muertes defends the Lucha Underground Championship against Prince Puma and Pentagon Jr. in a 3-Way Match.

episodes.name: Life After Death
episodes.overview: Fenix exchanges his Gift of the Gods Championship for a Lucha Underground Championship Match.  The Trios Titles are defended.

episodes.name: Aztec Warfare II
episodes.overview: Twenty luchadors compete for the Lucha Underground Championship in the second Aztec Warfare.

episodes.name: El Jefe is Back
episodes.overview: Dario Cueto returns and makes the champion defend his title.

episodes.name: Bird of War
episodes.overview: The Trios Tournament begins; Fenix faces the Monster Matanza Cueto for the championship; Famous B seeks his first client; Vampiro fights with his personal demons.

episodes.name: Three's a Crowd
episodes.overview: Rey Mysterio, Prince Puma and El Dragon Azteca Jr. must compete in the Trios Tournament; Dario Cueto redistributes the Seven Ancient Aztec Medallions and lets a new luchador compete for one. This episode features the musical guest El Conjunto Nueva Ola.

episodes.name: Monster Meets Monster
episodes.overview: Mil Muertes faces the Monster Matanza Cueto in a title match; an old rivalry is renewed over an Aztec Medallion. This episode features the musical guest El Conjunto Nueva Ola.

episodes.name: Cage in a Cage
episodes.overview: Johnny Mundo takes on Cage in a Steel Cage Match for an Aztec Medallion; four teams compete in the Trios Tournament Finals; Pentagon Jr. struggles with his injuries. This episode features the musical guest Bang Data.

episodes.name: No Mas
episodes.overview: Sexy Star battles Mariposa for an Aztec Medallion in the first "No Mas" match; Catrina confronts Dario Cueto; Luchadors have matches for the other available Medallions.

episodes.name: Graver Consequences
episodes.overview: Mil Muertes battles the Monster Matanza Cueto in a casket match for the Lucha Underground Championship; Triple Threat match between Joey Ryan, Cortez Castro and Mr.Cisco; Rey Mysterio Jr, Dragon Azteca Jr and Prince Puma defend their titles. This episode features the musical guest El Conjunto Nueva Ola.

episodes.name: Crime & Punishment
episodes.overview: Seven Luchadors compete for the Gift of the Gods Championship; Cage seeks revenge. This episode features the musical guest El Conjunto Nueva Ola.

episodes.name: Enter the Mundo
episodes.overview: Rey Mysterio, Prince Puma and El Dragon Azteca Jr. defend their Trios Championship; Joey Ryan and Cortez Castro's cover gets blown; The Gift of the Gods Championship is defended. This episode features the musical guest Voodoo Glow Skulls.

episodes.name: Judgement Day
episodes.overview: The Monster Matanza Cueto defends his title against the Gift of the Gods Champion; The Trios Champions defend their titles. Dragon Azteca Jr. searches for his mentor's killer. This episode features the musical guest Voodoo Glow Skulls.

episodes.name: The Contenders
episodes.overview: Drago & Aerostar face Jack Evans and PJ Black in a Nunchuck Match; Pentagon Jr. returns to the Temple. This episode features the musical guest Voodoo Glow Skulls.

episodes.name: Six to Survive
episodes.overview: Six luchadors compete in the first ever Six to Survive Match for a Championship Match at Ultima Lucha Dos. This episode features the musical guest Voodoo Glow Skulls.

episodes.name: Fame & Fortune
episodes.overview: The 7 Ancient Aztec Medallions are redistributed; Prince Puma addresses the Believers and reveals his plans for Ultima Lucha Dos; new luchador arrives at the Temple. This episode features the musical guest Voodoo Glow Skulls.

episodes.name: Phoenix, Dragon & Spaceman
episodes.overview: Dario Cueto announces a new opportunity that can be won at Ultima Lucha Dos; El Dragon Azteca faces Prince Puma. This episode features the musical guest El Conjunto Nueva Ola.

episodes.name: Ultima Lucha Dos: Part 1
episodes.overview: Son of Havoc, Cage, Texano and the Mack compete for a unique opportunity where the winner is faced with a career defining decision. This episode features the musical guest El Conjunto Nueva Ola.

episodes.name: Ultima Lucha Dos – Part 2
episodes.overview: King Cuerno faces Mil Muertes in a Death Match; 7 Way Gift of the Gods Elimination Match. This episode features the musical guest El Conjunto Nueva Ola.

episodes.name: Ultima Lucha Dos Part 3
episodes.overview: Rey Mysterio vs. Prince Puma; Pentagon vs. the Monster Matanza Cueto; Fenix, Drago and Aerostar vs. Worldwide Underground; Ivelisse vs. Taya; El Dragon Azteca Jr. vs. Black Lotus. This episode features the musical guest El Conjunto Nueva Ola.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: Darkness has taken over the temple. With the stakes higher than ever, the luchadores return to square off in combat. As a bevy of new competitors arrive, it will take more than honor and strength to remain on top at Lucha Underground.

episodes.name: Wheel of Misfortune
episodes.overview: The luchadors return to the temple where their fate will be determined by the spin of a wheel; Rey Mysterio competes.

episodes.name: The Amulet
episodes.overview: Killshot takes on Marty the Moth in the first Weapons of Mass Destruction Match; the power of an Aztec amulet is revealed.

episodes.name: Ultimate Opportunities
episodes.overview: The Dial of Doom selects an opponent for Matanza Cueto; Dario makes an announcement; Trios titles championship match.

episodes.name: Brothers in Broken Arms
episodes.overview: El Dragon Azteca Jr. battles against Chavo Guerrero with Rey Mysterio as the guest referee; The Worldwide Underground takes on the Trios Champions along with Sexy Star; Dario suspects Cortez Castro.

episodes.name: The Prince and the Monster
episodes.overview: Matanza gets another opponent; Ivelisse finds a new love; Killshot receives some news; The Rabbit Tribe is introduced.

episodes.name: The Open Road to Revenge
episodes.overview: Rey Mysterio vs Chavo Guerrero; Sexy Star vs Jack Evans; Son of Havoc and Mascarita Sagrada return with ravenous appetites for revenge.

episodes.name: Payback Time
episodes.overview: Prince Puma versus Mil Muertes; Johnny Mundo seeks a match with Sexy Star; Dial of Doom picks another opponent for Matanza.

episodes.name: Gifts of the Gods
episodes.overview: City Councilman Delgado arrives and gives Dario a gift; Sexy Star defends her title; Rey Mysterio asks Dario for a favor.

episodes.name: Loser Leaves Lucha
episodes.overview: Loser Leaves Town Match between Rey Mysterio and Chavo Guerrero; Dario gives the Dial of Doom a spin.

episodes.name: Ready for War
episodes.overview: Prince Puma and Mil Muertes in Graver Consequences; Mascarita Sagrada takes on Famous B in a Believer's Backlash Match.

episodes.name: Aztec Warfare III
episodes.overview: Twenty luchadores compete in Aztec Warfare for the Lucha Underground Championship.

episodes.name: Every Woman is Sexy, Every Woman is a Star
episodes.overview: A Lucha Underground Championship match; Black Lotus returns to the temple; The Rabbit Tribe arrives; Catrina confronts Jeremiah Crane.

episodes.name: Breaker of Bones
episodes.overview: Vampiro demands satisfaction from his former student; Pentagon Dark battles the Black Lotus Triad; Dario and Matanza have different plans.

episodes.name: The Bulls of Boyle Heights
episodes.overview: The Battle of the Bulls Tournament begins; Cortez Castro goes deeper undercover; Kobra Moon tells the history of her tribe.

episodes.name: En La Sombras
episodes.overview: The continuation of The Battle of the Bulls Tournament; El Dragon Azteca Jr. visits Rey Mysterio; Sexy Star is the target of mind games.

episodes.name: The Battle of the Bulls
episodes.overview: The tournament winner gets a title shot against the winner between Johnny Mundo and Sexy Star; Drago's fate is revealed.

episodes.name: The Gauntlet
episodes.overview: Cage and Texano continue their series; Jeremiah Crane wrestles Mil Muertes; a luchador returns for some revenge.

episodes.name: Evil Rising
episodes.overview: The Mack battles Johnny Mundo; Paul London and the Rabbit Tribe versus Kobra Moon and her reptiles.

episodes.name: Gods Among Men
episodes.overview: Johnny Mundo confronts The Mack about their championship match; El Dragon Azteca Jr. seeks a match with Matanza.

episodes.name: All Night Long... Again
episodes.overview: The Mack takes on Johnny Mundo in an All Night Long Match.

episodes.name: Sudden Death
episodes.overview: The Lucha Underground Championship is defended; Dario makes an announcement; Prince Puma versus Mil Muertes in a Boyles Height Street Fight.

episodes.name: The Cup Begins
episodes.overview: The Cueto Cup begins. Johnny Mundo and Rey Mysterio start their training; Cage visits Councilman Delgado.

episodes.name: Family First
episodes.overview: The Cueto Cup continues its first round; Marty the Moth continues his caddish ways; Rey Mysterio and Johnny Mundo ready themselves for their battle.

episodes.name: Macho Madness
episodes.overview: The Cueto Cup's first round continues; a new luchador arrives to the temple; Crane's jealously erupts.

episodes.name: Left for Dead
episodes.overview: Dante Fox flashbacks to being a POW; the first round of The Cueto Cup winds down; Rey Mysterio and Johnny Mundo continue their training.

episodes.name: A Fenix to a Flame
episodes.overview: The Cueto Cup's second round begins; Marty the Moth battles Fenix; Brenda pays a visit to Texano.

episodes.name: Fade to Black
episodes.overview: The Cueto Cup continues; Vampiro gives counsel to Prince Puma on his match; Johnny Mundo introduces his agent to the Worldwide Underground.

episodes.name: Booyaka! Booyaka!
episodes.overview: Rey Mysterio battles PJ Black; the Cueto Cup continues with its second round; Son of Madness confronts Son of Havoc.

episodes.name: The Hunger Inside
episodes.overview: The Cueto Cup's quarterfinals begin; Dario admonishes Matanza; Marty the Moth continues with his unscrupulous behavior towards Melissa.

episodes.name: Bloodlines
episodes.overview: The Cueto Cup's quarterfinals continue; an FBI agent visits Dario Cueto.

episodes.name: The Cup Runneth Over
episodes.overview: Rey Mysterio and Johnny Mundo have a confrontation.The semifinalists compete; Catrina has her eyes on Cage's Gauntlet.

episodes.name: The Cueto Cup
episodes.overview: The finalists battle for the Cueto Cup. Rey Mysterio vs Johnny Mundo for the Lucha Underground Championship.

episodes.name: Havoc Running Wild
episodes.overview: Son of Madness and Son of Havoc's feud intensifies; Joey Ryan antagonizes Cortez Castro.

episodes.name: Career Opportunities
episodes.overview: Castro versus Ryan in a Five-O Street Fight; Johnny Mundo challenges Prince Puma at Ultima Lucha; Dario makes an announcement.

episodes.name: Cien
episodes.overview: Atomicos match; El Dragon Azteca Jr. versus Pentagon Dark; Rey Mysterio versus Matanza.

episodes.name: The Rise of the Ring Announcer
episodes.overview: Marty the Moth teams with Mariposa to take on Fenix and Melissa Santos; a seven-way Gift of the Gods title match.

episodes.name: Ultima Lucha Tres: Part 1
episodes.overview: Killshot versus Dante Fox in The Hell of War match. Famous B competes.

episodes.name: Ultima Lucha Tres: Part 2
episodes.overview: Fenix versus Marty the Moth in a Hair vs Mask match; Ivelisse battles Catrina.

episodes.name: Ultima Lucha Tres: Part 3
episodes.overview: Sexy Star battles Taya in a Last Luchadora standing match.

episodes.name: Ultima Lucha Tres: Part 4
episodes.overview: El Dragon Azteca Jr. versus Matanza in a steel cage match; Jeremiah Crane battles Mil Muertes; Prince Puma tangles with Johnny Mundo.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: Now that Dario Cueto has been released from prison after being arrested for the murder of Mr. Cisco, the mysterious Lucha Underground Temple is back in business. Dario is more confident than ever in his brother, the undefeated Lucha Underground Champion, the Monster Matanza Cueto and his quest for violent domination and the destruction of the seven ancient Aztec tribes. Now while one hero must take a dark path, others will have to make even greater sacrifices if they hope to save themselves and the world.

episodes.name: El Jefe
episodes.overview: The Lucha Underground Temple moves to a new location and Pentagon Dark must defend his Lucha Underground Championship for the very first time; Dario Cueto's fate is revealed.

episodes.name: Darkness and the Monster
episodes.overview: Catrina hopes to restore her life and searches for the Gauntlet of the Gods. The Trios Champions defend their titles against three new fighters and one of the Seven Ancient Aztec Medallions comes back into play.

episodes.name: Rest in Pieces
episodes.overview: Johnny Mundo and the Worldwide Underground plot revenge. Jack Evans issues a Put Up or Shut Up Challenge. A new challenger comes for the Lucha Underground Champion. Fenix takes on Jeremiah Crane and Mil Muertes in a Three-Way to the Grave match.

episodes.name: Pain Love and Sacrifice
episodes.overview: Catrina gives Melissa a gift; Johnny Mundo and Taya take on Kobra Moon and her King, Daga; Antonio gives King Cuerno the chance for revenge and the chance to win an Ancient Aztec Medallion; the Monster Matanza Cueto makes a Sacrifice to the Gods.

episodes.name: Sacrificio
episodes.overview: Mil Muertes takes on Cage in one of three matches for Ancient Aztec Mediallions; Matanza makes another Sacrifice to the Gods; Mascarita Sagrada takes Paul London and the Rabbit Tribe to finally meet the legendary White Rabbit.

episodes.name: Break the Machine
episodes.overview: Paul London battles newcomer Dezmond X for the Final Ancient Aztec Medallion; Johnny Mundo takes on the Giant Snake Man; Vibora. Jack Evans scouts XO Lishus; Cage does battle with Pentagon Dark.

episodes.name: The Gift That Keeps on Giving
episodes.overview: A new Gift of the Gods Champion is crowned; Mariposa motivates her broken-armed brother Marty “The Moth” Martinez; Sammy Guevara looks for revenge against “the Savage” Jake Strong.

episodes.name: The Ranks of the Reptiles
episodes.overview: The rivalry between the Worldwide Underground and the Reptile Tribe escalates and the stakes are raised in the war between the two factions; The Mack suffers a haunting experience; Pentagon and Cage must find partners.

episodes.name: A Match Made in Heaven
episodes.overview: Mariposa makes a proposal to Antonio Cueto; Paul London makes an offering to the Gods on behalf of the White Rabbit; The Worldwide Underground take on The Reptile Tribe in an Atomicos Match; if the Reptiles win, Johnny must join them.

episodes.name: A Snake Scorned
episodes.overview: Paul London attempts to satisfy the White Rabbit; tensions between the Trios Champions are at an all-time high as they are forced to defend their titles against a dangerous opponent; Cage and Pentagon Dark’s conflict explodes.

episodes.name: Last Man or Machine Standing
episodes.overview: Pentagon Dark battles Cage for the Lucha Underground Championship; The Mack vs. Mil Muertes in the first ever Haunted House Match; Johnny and Taya have a wedding shower; Rosa continues to have an influence on Ricky.

episodes.name: Till Death Do Us Part
episodes.overview: Johnny Mundo and Taya get married and their nuptials are filled with lots of surprises; XO Lishus takes on Jack Evans in a "No Mas" Match; Drago battles "The Savage" Jake Strong.

episodes.name: The Circle of Life
episodes.overview: Melissa Santos and Catrina engage in an epic confrontation; the Monster Matanza Cueto makes another Sacrifice to the Gods; a Luchador seeking revenge comes after Pentagon Dark; Son of Havoc observes Killshot's match.

episodes.name: Pet Cemetery
episodes.overview: Fenix returns to the Temple to team with Drago and Aerostar against the Reptile Tribe; King Cuerno wants a Lucha Underground Championship Match, but he's not the only one; the Gift of the Gods Championship is defended.

episodes.name: The Hunted
episodes.overview: The Lucha Underground Championship and Gift of the Gods Championship are both defended; Melissa Santos and Aerostar notice a change in Fenix; Paul London pays another visit to the White Rabbit.

episodes.name: Kill Mil
episodes.overview: Ivelisse and XO Lishus find a new partner to help them face the Reptile Tribe; Jake Strong takes on Drago and Aero Star in a Nunchuck Match; a new number one contender for the Lucha Underground Championship is determined.

episodes.name: The Moth and the Butterfly
episodes.overview: The Rabbit Tribe takes on XO Lishus, Ivelisse and Joey Ryan; Marty "The Moth" Martinez introduces a new associate and sends a message to his Ultima Lucha opponent; Killshot and Son of Havoc finally go one on one.

episodes.name: Spiders and Skeletons
episodes.overview: Taya Mundo returns for revenge; Ricky Mundo makes a shocking confession; two of Lucha Underground's fiercest rivals Mil Muertes and Fenix must team to take on their Ultima Lucha opponents.

episodes.name: Savagery
episodes.overview: Jake Strong talks with Cueto and makes demands; a Gift of the Gods Battle Royale takes place; The Mack battles his friend and former Trios Partner Killshot; a huge main event is made.

episodes.name: Seven to Survive
episodes.overview: Seven Luchadors do battle in a Seven to Survive Elimination Match for the Gift of the Gods Championship; Johnny Mundo gets some help, preparing for his match against the Monster Matanza Cueto.

episodes.name: Ultima Lucha Cuatro Pt. 1
episodes.overview: Aerostar pays a visit to an old friend; 3-Way Trios Championship Elimination Match; Taya Mundo takes on Ricky Mundo; Son of Havoc battles Killshot in match where the loser must unmask.

episodes.name: Ultima Lucha Cuatro Pt. 2
episodes.overview: El Dragon Azteca Jr. vs. Fenix; The Mack vs. Mil Muertes in a Death Match; Johnny Mundo vs. Matanza; Pentagón Dark vs. Marty "The Moth" in a Cero Miedo Match; The Order sets their plan in motion to destroy the Seven Aztec Tribes.
